# Report Source Contract Sync

When adding, removing, or renaming report sources under `backend/app/features/reports/sources/**`:

1. Keep source keys synchronized across:
   - backend `ReportSourceKey` (`backend/app/schema/report.py`)
   - frontend `ReportSourceKey` (`frontend/src/api/reports.ts`)
   - report source registry (`build_sources`)
2. Validate metadata generation succeeds for all registered sources.
3. Add or update a backend contract test that fails on registry/literal drift.
4. Include the contract test in CI and keep it green in the same change set.
